memory_text = "GWEN DOYLE logs twenty-seven aboard, then crosses out the printed route to Tollard. 'The signs say east. Road control says west. I can see the school from here, so we are going to the school.' A child asks if that is allowed. Gwen says, 'It is my bus.' Twenty-seven names are checked in at Ashmere School."
